# thoth_webhook_settings

Manages outbound webhook enablement, destination URL, and signing secret.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_webhook_settings" "alerts" {
  webhook_enabled       = true
  webhook_url           = var.webhook_url
  webhook_secret        = var.webhook_secret
  test_webhook_on_apply = true
}
```
